sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist<br/>(Jupyter Notebook / Script)
    participant SDK as CodeFlare SDK<br/>(Python Client)
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant KubeRay as KubeRay Operator
    participant Kueue as Kueue Controller
    participant Dashboard as Ray Dashboard<br/>443/TCP HTTPS (via Route/HTTPRoute)
    participant RayHead as Ray Head Pod<br/>10001/TCP gRPC mTLS

    Note over User,RayHead: Flow 1: Interactive Cluster Lifecycle

    User->>SDK: Cluster(ClusterConfiguration(...))
    SDK->>K8sAPI: List LocalQueues (kueue.x-k8s.io/v1beta1)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>SDK: LocalQueue list (validate queue exists)

    User->>SDK: cluster.apply()
    SDK->>K8sAPI: Server-Side Apply RayCluster CR (ray.io/v1)<br/>Field Manager: codeflare-sdk<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>SDK: RayCluster created/updated
    K8sAPI->>KubeRay: Watch event: RayCluster created
    KubeRay->>K8sAPI: Create head pod, worker pods, services<br/>Auth: Service Account

    opt Kueue Integration
        K8sAPI->>Kueue: Watch event: RayCluster with queue label
        Kueue->>K8sAPI: Create Workload, manage admission
    end

    User->>SDK: cluster.wait_ready()
    loop Poll until ready
        SDK->>K8sAPI: Get RayCluster status<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8sAPI-->>SDK: RayCluster status (Ready/Suspended/Failed)
    end

    SDK->>K8sAPI: Read CA Secret ({cluster}-ca-secret-*)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>SDK: CA cert + private key
    SDK->>SDK: Generate client TLS cert<br/>(RSA 3072-bit, SHA-256, SAN entries)

    SDK->>K8sAPI: List HTTPRoutes (gateway.networking.k8s.io/v1)<br/>by label ray.io/cluster-name<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>SDK: HTTPRoute with Gateway ref
    SDK->>K8sAPI: Get Gateway hostname<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>SDK: Gateway hostname

    loop Dashboard readiness check
        SDK->>Dashboard: GET https://{host}/ray/{ns}/{name}<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        Dashboard-->>SDK: 200 OK
    end

    User->>RayHead: ray.init(address, runtime_env)<br/>gRPC mTLS (client cert)
    RayHead-->>User: Connected to Ray cluster

    Note over User,RayHead: Flow 2: RayJob Submission

    User->>SDK: RayJob(RayJobConfiguration(...))
    User->>SDK: rayjob.submit()

    opt Local files to upload
        SDK->>SDK: Zip working directory, base64-encode
        SDK->>K8sAPI: Create Secret ({job}-files)<br/>with ownerRef to RayJob<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    end

    SDK->>K8sAPI: Create RayJob CR (ray.io/v1)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>SDK: RayJob created
    K8sAPI->>KubeRay: Watch event: RayJob created

    alt Ephemeral Cluster
        KubeRay->>K8sAPI: Create RayCluster from embedded spec
    else Existing Cluster
        KubeRay->>K8sAPI: Select cluster via clusterSelector
    end

    KubeRay->>RayHead: Submit job to Ray Dashboard<br/>HTTP 8265/TCP (in-cluster)
    RayHead-->>KubeRay: Job submitted

    loop Status polling
        User->>SDK: rayjob.status()
        SDK->>K8sAPI: Get RayJob status<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8sAPI-->>SDK: RayJob status (Running/Succeeded/Failed)
    end
